summary:
Broad experience in the field of Information management with local Governemental organisations. Since 2007 specialised in Information management with Archival institutions, especially the development of strategies for long term preservation and long term disclosure of digital information.

Specialties: Preservation strategy, Projectmanagement, Changemanagement, implementation of new strategies
